# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Defense Tapboard — Environment Configuration
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values.
#
# VITE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL
#   The deployed Google Apps Script Web App URL.
#   Get this from the Apps Script editor → Deploy → Manage deployments.
#   Example: https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbx.../exec
#
#   If left blank or missing, the app works fully offline with
#   local persistence only — sync features will be disabled.
#
#   The DESTINATION spreadsheet is NOT configured here.
#   Users configure their Google Sheet URL, tab names, and
#   registration key directly inside the app (Setup page →
#   Google Sheets Connection). This env variable only sets the
#   generic Apps Script endpoint that handles all write requests.
VITE_APPS_SCRIPT_URL=
